    "(f) The combination of deep neural network and hyperspectral image prior network forms the overall architecture of hyperspectral image reconstruction.",
    "With the help of this network, the experiment reconstructed hyperspectral images of 25 spectral channels from 460 nm to 700 nm.",
    "Reproduced from [208].",
    "Copyright 2023, Elsevier.end-to-end algorithm, the experiments demonstrated better hyperspectral reconstruction results compared to traditional separate optimization methods, showing significant advantages in terms of average peak signal-to-noise ratio (PSNR).",
    "AI techniques automate and optimize each step, simplifying the process and improving efficiency, leading to remarkable advancements in metasurface imaging systems, potentially becoming the next generation of high-quality cameras."
